Two people did not survive the crash
Two people were travelling in the plane, a man (†63) and a woman (†38). "The plane asked for permission to land at the Chaloupky airport near Klatovy at 8.30 p.m.," said police spokeswoman Dana Ladmanová. That was also the last entry, and at that time it was supposed to be near Vojovice, near Žinkovy, according to GPS coordinates.
