14.6 If a Patch Delivery fails to meet the acceptance criteria set out in Appendix 9 (Acceptance Procedure) the Acceptance Procedure shall be terminated as unsuccessful and the Client shall make an inventory of the defects that have been manifested in the Patch Delivery submitted for the Acceptance Procedure and return this inventory, together with the Patch Delivery, to the Contractor.
